@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.75)) - ((v0 + 0.15 - v1 + 0.54) - (tmp + 0.07 * v2 + 0.41)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.16 + 0.89))
    tmp = (0.59 - wp.exp((v0 + 1.00 - v2 + 0.46)))
    data[tid] = v0
